description:
Discover the purpose and heart behind the book, “The Omega Rebellion” as author Rick Howard shares how he was urged by the Spirit of God to communicate a message about the use of ancient mystical practices. He shares how God has orchestrated events to confirm he was moving in the right direction. Learn how God spoke through His Word, His Spirit and providence to Rick Howard as he wrote “The Omega Rebellion” over a grueling five-year period of listening, researching, waiting, and—finally—writing.

Discover more:
